The paper focuses on understanding user reactions to news sources on social media platforms, which involves analyzing social interactions and language use. This suggests that the paper could fall under the categories of social networks (cs.SOC), social media (cs.SI), natural language processing (cs.CL), cybersecurity (cs.CYBER), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
